modules.description: This module handles cryptographic operations for secure software updates, including key generation, message signing, and signature verification. It works with base64-encoded public keys, secret keys, and signatures, producing and validating cryptographic fingerprints. Concrete use cases include verifying downloaded artifacts and generating key pairs for release signing.

This module implements cryptographic operations for secure software updates, including key generation, message signing, and signature verification. It works with base64-encoded public keys, secret keys, and signatures to produce and validate cryptographic fingerprints. Use it to verify downloaded artifacts or generate key pairs for release signing.
